title: NEW SHOW AT VICTORIA FARM MAY 15TH-17TH 2015

posts.content:
If after the AGM you've not had enough of us we are hosting a VW AIRCOOLED show at V/F. I always said I'd now only do the AGM but after talking to the organizers this seems to have the making of a brilliant family show. There will be traders, entertainment, food stalls music and much more. There will be of course a bar in the barn/marquee at pub prices hosting real ales etc.
For booking and any more information look up VW HANGOUT. Will be looking forward to seeing you at the bar to carry on where we left off at the AGM!
regards Eddy.

Looks like just Us then Lol

Website is www.Vwhangout.co.uk
